        "code": "function render(ctx, time, params, canvas) {\n  const { width, height } = canvas;\n  const centerX = width / 2;\n  const centerY = height / 2;\n\n  // 计算方块尺寸（基于画布短边的比例）\n  const size = Math.min(width, height) * params.blockSize;\n\n  // 计算旋转角度\n  // time 从 0 到 duration 循环，实现无限循环\n  // 除以 3000 是为了让默认速度下 3 秒转一圈\n  const angle = (time / 3000) * Math.PI * 2 * params.rotationSpeed;\n\n  ctx.save();\n  \n  // 移动坐标系到画布中心\n  ctx.translate(centerX, centerY);\n  \n  // 旋转坐标系\n  ctx.rotate(angle);\n  \n  // 绘制方块（以中心为原点）\n  ctx.fillStyle = params.blockColor;\n  ctx.fillRect(-size / 2, -size / 2, size, size);\n  \n  ctx.restore();\n}\n\nwindow.__motionRender = render;",
        "createdAt": 1768547946065,
        "updatedAt": 1768550341658
